displayName.english: Are the subjects able to move?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は移動できているか？

description.english: Subject understands basic operational movements.
description.japanese: 被験者は基本操作移動を理解している。

displayName.english: Are the subjects able to jump?
displayName.japanese: 被験者はジャンプできているか？

description.english: Subject understands basic maneuvers and jumps.
description.japanese: 被験者は基本操作ジャンプを理解している。

displayName.english: Did the subjects enjoy the cherry blossom spring?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は春の桜吹雪を満喫したか？

description.english: The subject walked through a floor where cherry blossoms were scattered with a spring atmosphere.
description.japanese: 被験者は春の雰囲気漂う桜舞い散るフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Did the subjects enjoy their summer vacations?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は夏のバケーションを満喫したか？

description.english: The subjects walked through the floor under the scorching sun with a summer atmosphere.
description.japanese: 被験者は夏の雰囲気漂う炎天下のフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Did the subjects enjoy the fall of appetite?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は食欲の秋を満喫したか？

description.english: The subjects walked through the floor of autumn leaves with an autumn atmosphere.
description.japanese: 被験者は秋の雰囲気漂う舞い散る紅葉のフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Did the subjects enjoy the winter snow?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は冬の雪を満喫したか？

description.english: Subject traversed a snowy floor.
description.japanese: 被験者は雪降るフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Did the subject complete the experiment?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は実験を完遂したか？

description.english: Subjects patiently traversed all floors of the experiment.
description.japanese: 被験者は忍耐強く実験の全てのフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Did the subject patiently complete the second experiment?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は忍耐強く2回目の実験を完遂したか？

description.english: The researchers were surprised by the subject's completion of the second experiment.
description.japanese: 被験者の2回目の実験完遂に研究者は驚いている。

displayName.english: What drives the subject?
displayName.japanese: 被験者を突き動かすものは何か？

description.english: The researchers are surprised by the subject's unexpected completion of the fifth experiment.
description.japanese: 研究者は被験者の予想外の5回目の実験完遂に驚いている。

displayName.english: Did the subject complete the experiment at an unexpected speed?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は予想外のスピードで実験を完遂したか？

description.english: Subjects completed the experiment within one hour. Researchers are rushing to analyze the data.
description.japanese: 被験者は1時間以内に実験を完遂した。研究者はデータの分析を急いでいる。

displayName.english: Can you see any abnormalities in the subjects?
displayName.japanese: 被験者に異常を確認できるか？

description.english: The subject completed the case within 20 minutes. The researchers are concerned about the subjects' obsession with the experiment and are considering stopping the experiment.
description.japanese: 被験者は20分以内に事件を完遂した。研究者は被験者の実験への執着に懸念を抱き、実験の中止を検討している。

displayName.english: Rank S
displayName.japanese: ランクS

description.english: Excellent. In 900 sec.
description.japanese: 極上！900秒以内クリア

displayName.english: Rank A
displayName.japanese: ランクA

description.english: Outstanding. In 1800 sec.
description.japanese: 特筆すべき1800秒クリア

displayName.english: Rank B
displayName.japanese: ランクB

description.english: Great. In 3600 sec.
description.japanese: 素晴らしい3600秒クリア

displayName.english: Rank C
displayName.japanese: ランクC

description.english: Impressive. In 4800 sec.
description.japanese: 印象的な4800秒クリア

displayName.english: Rank D
displayName.japanese: ランクD

description.english: Well done
description.japanese: 努力のクリア

displayName.english: Will the subject challenge a new realm?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は新たな領域に挑むか？

description.english: Welcome to a new mode that pushes your brain to its limits.
description.japanese: 脳を酷使する新しいモードに挑戦を歓迎する。

displayName.english: Will the test subject enjoy subtle changes?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は小さな変化を楽しむか？

description.english: Take pleasure in familiar places with slight differences.
description.japanese: 見たことのある場所だが少し変わっていることを楽しむ。

displayName.english: Will the subject race through late spring?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は晩春を駆け抜けるか？

description.english: The subject conquered the Late Spring Floor while feeling the approach of summer.
description.japanese: 被験者は夏の訪れを感じながら晩春のフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Will the subject sweat in the midsummer heat?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は真夏に汗をかくか？

description.english: Drenched in sweat like a waterfall, the subject conquered the Midsummer Floor.
description.japanese: 滝のような汗をかいて真夏のフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: What does the subject ponder on an autumn night?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は秋の夜長に何を思うか？

description.english: While gazing at the autumn leaves, the subject conquered the Autumn Moon Floor.
description.japanese: 被験者は紅葉を見ながら秋月のフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: Do the subject's fingers grow numb from the cold?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は寒さで指が悴むか？

description.english: Awakened by the chill, the subject conquered the Winter Dawn Floor.
description.japanese: 被験者は寒さで目を覚まし冬暁のフロアを踏破した。

displayName.english: What does the subject feel upon completing the experiment?
displayName.japanese: 被験者が実験を終えた時に感じるものとは？

description.english: Cleared Hard Mode once. Report what you feel after completing the new experiment.
description.japanese: ハードモード1回クリア。新たな実験を終えた後に感じるものを報告せよ。

displayName.english: Will the subject continue the experiment without motivation?
displayName.japanese: 被験者は動機なく実験を続けるのか？

description.english: Cleared Hard Mode 5 times. A proactive approach to new challenges is highly welcomed.
description.japanese: ハードモード5回クリア。新しい提示に対して積極的に取り込む姿勢を歓迎する。

displayName.japanese: ハードモード ランクB

description.english: Cleared "Ultimate Technique" in 2400 seconds.
description.japanese: 超絶技巧の2400秒クリア

displayName.japanese: ハードモード ランクC

description.japanese: 努力の3600秒クリア
